    "Finally, in the calculation phase, the collected execution times and path information are aggregated to compute the final WCET estimate.",
    "This method avoids the need for explicit hardware modeling, enhances portability, and automates test-data generation.",
    "Betts et al. [74] propose a novel method to conduct WCET analysis by combining hardware-based trace collection with source-level analysis.",
    "Traditional WCET analysis methods using instrumentation introduce a probe effect that affects timing accuracy.",
    "To overcome this, the authors leverage modern hardware trace capabilities to gather execution traces at the object-code level without intrusive instrumentation."
